---
3md: 1.0
title: Fallback
model: claude-haiku-4-5
---
@plane z=0 label="Fallback"
# Fallback
No plane is marked kind=identity, so the first plane (lowest z) is the identity
by the fallback rule. RULE: valid (fallback identity).

@plane z=1 label="echo" kind=skill triggers="echo, repeat, say"
# Skill: echo
Repeat the input back to the user.
